'''Weechee''' was a common name among [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Gender/Legends|females]]. According to Ewok legend, a cruel [[Prince/Legends|princess]] named Weechee married a handsome [[Prince/Legends|prince]], only to discover that he was an evil night-spirit.

